hits.definition:
笔 (F 筆)

[bǐ] writing implement;

    毛笔 máobǐ brush;

    钢笔 gāngbǐ pen;

    铅笔 qiānbǐ pencil

夏

[xià] (= 夏天 xiàtiān) summer;

    春夏秋冬 chūnxiàqiūdōng the four seasons

福

[fú] blessing, good fortune, (= 幸福 xìngfú) happiness, happy;

    祝福 zhùfú invoke/wish a blessing;

    福建 Fújiàn

{ It is common to hang calligraphy of this character up-side-down on doors,

in order to get people to note that 福倒了 fú dàole = "The 'Fu' is up-side-down",

which is pronounced just as 福到了 = "Fortune/happiness has come" }
